    <p>Verify your previous purchase of DRMeter to upgrade at a special price.</p>

    <div class="form-row align-items-center mb-3 row">
    <div class="input-group col-lg-9 col-xl-7">
    <span class="input-group-addon border-secondary d-none d-md-block">Your license code</span>
